{"tid":2378104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"群星輪住祝賀丨秀智性感晒舞技賀出道十周年","createTime":"2021-01-24T07:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T09:48:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"51bba9f8e17cb31398e3c9e7975c5bb55e753b3b","tid":2378104,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6CkERTtfBsxcbLr_f-XZti27uu8=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YZC4BXK4INBTBOYW2NLLBPNMSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6CkERTtfBsxcbLr_f-XZti27uu8%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYZC4BXK4INBTBOYW2NLLBPNMSY.jpg&h=c067d542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國「國民初戀」秀智於2010年以miss A的成員出道，不過組合於2017年宣佈解散，而前年秀智加盟Management SOOP事務所，做孔劉的師妹。雖然簽約新公司後，秀智就專注演戲方面工作，但她亦沒有忘記歌迷，原定上月透過kakao tv進行網上直播fans見面會《Suzy: A Tempo》，與fans共賀出道十周年，但受疫情影響，網上見面會事務所延期至昨日舉行。<br />\n<br />\n人緣甚好<br />\n秀智曾拍過多部電視劇，昨日見面會上更獲一眾拍檔拍片賀她出道十周年，當中包括去年拍畢的《Start-Up：我的新創時代》兩位拍檔南柱赫和金宣虎，還有《亡徒覓雪》的李昇基和申成祿等，就連前東主、JYP老闆朴震榮都有拍片賀秀智，可見秀智人緣甚好。當中朴震榮壓軸登場，於片段中表示：「這麼快就10周年了，真的很驚訝。 過去10年間努力活動，一直都很善良，非常感謝，希望今後的10年更加帥氣，以後也要加油。」令秀智大為感動。<br />\n<br />\n力谷《Wonderland》<br />\n另外，於見面會上秀智亦展示其多才多藝的一面，除了穿上性感服飾又唱又跳外，亦有彈結他自彈自唱。秀智談到被冠以「國民初戀」的稱號，她就說：「現在回想起來，真是非常感謝，當時並沒有那麼覺得，可能因為十分忙碌，而且行程亦十分緊湊。」對於作為演員如何選擇作品時，秀智表示：「無論選擇甚麼樣的作品，都想融入到那個作品的角色中去，一直努力真誠地去演繹，非常感謝大家在《Start-Up》中對徐達美這個角色的喜愛，期待下次通過《Wonderland》以不同的角色同大家見面，希望大家多多喜愛作為演員的秀智。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x9r7Ovcu54uVPF5FBTZsyFDF16A=/802x2676/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OSGDC2A6DVEX7JTU4FQHCAQ5NU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx9r7Ovcu54uVPF5FBTZsyFDF16A%3D%2F802x2676%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOSGDC2A6DVEX7JTU4FQHCAQ5NU.jpg&h=ecd04f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7ZkA8IKLlzaTTw6DM_I_CSQ94bw=/802x2705/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZCIPKP56Z5CBHPMKCW6663D5AM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7ZkA8IKLlzaTTw6DM_I_CSQ94bw%3D%2F802x2705%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZCIPKP56Z5CBHPMKCW6663D5AM.jpg&h=4095074f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afe6fb342827a32eb81c3858fb4bc3d3cb3149eb","tid":2378104,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:45:29.000Z","msg":"正式過彩好多..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e042505b59a06510f6ef7d1697c35c33868248","tid":2378104,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"正到痴線...."},{"pid":"b85e0fac732346e0d615a54fccaa602c8c8e67a2","tid":2378104,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afe6fb342827a32eb81c3858fb4bc3d3cb3149eb","tid":2378104,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:45:29.000Z","msg":"正式過彩好多..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:48:54.000Z","msg":"休想取代彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d355853ba1bfff8ab0a65ebf31f5ad1199cf69a4","tid":2378104,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0e042505b59a06510f6ef7d1697c35c33868248","tid":2378104,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"正到痴線...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/IdleDeliriousKitten-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FIdleDeliriousKitten-size_restric